## Tests

вњ… **Vitest** dla unit + integration tests
вњ… **Co-located** `*.test.ts` obok source files (preferred) lub `__test__/`
вњ… **describe / it / expect** structure
вњ… **Polish character tests** wszД™dzie gdzie text input handling

```typescript
describe("slugify", () => {
  it("handles Polish diacritics", () => {
    expect(slugify("ЕЃГіdЕє ЕјГіЕ‚w")).toBe("lodz-zolw");
  });
});
```

## Anti-patterns

вќЊ **`any` type** вЂ” use `unknown` + type guards lub Zod
вќЊ **`as` casts** вЂ” use type guards lub schema validation
вќЊ **Empty catch blocks** вЂ” at least log z context
вќЊ **Mutable global state** вЂ” pass via context lub use module-scoped const
вќЊ **Magic numbers** w code вЂ” extract do `const MAX_X = 100`
вќЊ **Console.log w production code** вЂ” use ctx.logger lub structured logger

## Patterns

вњ… **Dependency injection via context**:
```typescript
interface SkillContext {
  readonly llm: LLMProvider;
  readonly logger: Logger;
  readonly outputWriter: AtomicWriter;
}
```

вњ… **Pure functions where possible** вЂ” easier testing, better composability.

